tourBios.carHigh: 2015: Was atop the leaderboard after 18 holes at the Florida Qualifying Tournament before a third-round 77 dropped him to T34. Closed Sunday with a 65 to finish T15. Made four cuts in eight events with best top-25 finish (T22) coming early at the PC Financial Open in May.
tourBios.personal: Biggest thrill outside golf is playing baseball...Diehard Dallas sports fan...Volunteers at Habitat For Humanity...His dream foursome would include members of his family...Hopes to play Augusta National one day.

dyn.dynResults: His best finish on the Mackenzie Tour-PGA T was T22nd in 2015 at the PC Financial Open.
dyn.dynStats: He ranks T43rd in Par Breakers on the Mackenzie Tour-PGA TOUR Canada.
